        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>This black pearl sparkles with light. The resonant power allows you to cast <a class=\"entity-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-pack=\"pf2e.spells-srd\" data-id=\"R9xqCBblkS5KE4y7\"> Sending</a> once per day.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">R</span> envision</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> you are targeted by a mental effect</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong>&nbsp;You receive a +4 status bonus to your saving throw against the triggering effect.</p>\n<p>Whether or not your save is successful, the aeon stone attempts a counteract check at <a class=\"inline-roll roll\" title=\"1d20+30\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d20+30\"> 1d20+30</a> to immediately reflect a copy of the effect back at the originator, targeting it using the creature&rsquo;s own relevant statistics but controlling the effect as if you had cast it.</p>\n<p>Every time you activate this aeon stone, attempt a DC 5 flat check. On a failure, the stone shatters and loses its magical properties forever.</p>\n<p><a class=\"entity-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-pack=\"pf2e.spell-effects\" data-id=\"p2aGtovaY1feytws\"> Effect: Aeon Stone (Black Pearl)</a></p>"
